  "original_title": "\u0d9c\u0dd0\u0db6\u0dd2\u0dd2\u0db1\u0dd2 \u0db8\u0dc0\u0dca\u0dc0\u0dbb\u0dd4\u0db1\u0dca\u0da7 \u0d85\u0db8\u0dad\u0dbb \u0dbb\u0dd4.2500\u0d9a\u0dca - \u0d86\u0dc4\u0dcf\u0dbb \u0db1\u0ddc\u0db8\u0dd0\u0dad\u0dd2 \u0db4\u0dc0\u0dd4\u0dbd\u0d9a\u0da7 \u0db8\u0dc3\u0d9a\u0da7 \u0dbb\u0dd4 10000\u0d9a\u0dca",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Additional Rs.2500 for pregnant mothers - Rs.10000 per month for a food insecure family",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "President Ranil Wickramasinghe said that instead of the current allowance of 20000 rupees, an additional monthly allowance of 2500 rupees will be given to pregnant mothers.",
        "The President said that 10,000 rupees per month will be provided to these families in the coming period of the year for 61,000 families who do not have food security.",
        "The President also said that subsidies will be given to small fishing vessel owners and estate families who do not have electricity facilities."
      ],
